cs.DC, cs.LG, cs.AI, cs.SE, cs.PL 

This paper introduces a system that extends TensorFlow's semantics to provide support for a broader variety of application logic. It focuses on the execution of machine learning applications and targets cloud computing frameworks. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing). The paper also discusses the dataflow graph and the execution of application logic, which are related to cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence). Additionally, the paper introduces a new system that modifies the existing TensorFlow runtime, which is related to cs.SE (Software Engineering) and cs.PL (Programming Languages).
